track_notes: A track from April 2014 submitted on behalf of Terry G0VWP.
track_title: Broomy Law from the A702 road

track_notes: Drove cautiously into farmyard (large cattle sheds) no one to ask about parking - it was dark. Track to comms site on Broomy Law was followed using headlamp (no vehicular access). 20 mins to the summit. Experienced RF interference affecting the control of my HF transceiver which restricted my activity. Suggest if you can that you operate some distance away from the equipment compounds.
